section.literallayout:
Literal block
Do handle all types of special characters, just as they are, like those tokenizer regular expressions:
array ( 1 => '(\A(?P<value>[ 	]+))S', 2 => '(\A(?P<value>
||
))S', 4 => '(\A(?P<value>([!"#$%&'()*+,./:;<=>?@[\]^_`{|}~-]|\xe2\x80\xa2|\xe2\x80\xa3|\xe2\x81\x83)\2*))S', 3 => '(\A(?P<value>\))S', 5 => '(\A(?P<value>(?: [^`*_\[\]|()"':.
	 ]|[^`*_\[\]|()"':.
	 ])+))S', )
